### cargo-fuzz ###
# Build outputs and crash artefacts produced by `cargo +nightly fuzz run`.
fuzz/target/
fuzz/artifacts/
fuzz/coverage/

# libfuzzer-generated corpus entries — 40-character lowercase-hex
# SHA1 filenames. The hand-picked regression seeds
# (`connection_preface`, `data_frame`,
# `crash-d7a34a0d-padded-headers-underflow-regression`, …) use
# alphanumeric / kebab-cased names and stay tracked. Each `[0-9a-f]`
# below is one hex character; together they require an exact 40-char
# lowercase-hex name, so seed files are unaffected.
fuzz/corpus/*/[0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f][0-9a-f]

